ch.bfh.ti.gravis.core.graph.item

Class AbstractGraphItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.bfh.ti.gravis.core.graph.item.AbstractEditItemObservable
      • ch.bfh.ti.gravis.core.graph.item.AbstractGraphItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEditItemObservable, IGraphItem, IRestrictedGraphItem
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GravisEdge, GravisVertex

    public abstract class AbstractGraphItem
extends AbstractEditItemObservable
implements IGraphItem
    This basic implementation of the IGraphItem interface gives access to common methods on vertices and edges.
    Author:
    Patrick Kofmel (kofmp1@bfh.ch)
